站在别人面前时，他们总要说，“诶你怎么那么没精神啊”“你怎么不说话啊”“你看起来不是很高兴的样子”。 有时候心里难受我也试着找别人倾诉，父母也不是很懂我，关系一般的朋友我也不好意思找人家谈（当然有个别小天使非常暖心啦❤️）。跟一个很要好的人谈过后发现我俩思维根本不在一个频道上，就是，她理解不了我为什么不敢说话，甚至没有说话的欲望，我也理解不了她。再说下去没有任何意义，后来我也不去找别人发牢骚了。 但是那些让我焦虑的社交场合到处都是，怎么做才能缓解？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Im833wYDAzMsJEAMaCTEwOTE4NTc5NCDa/K+0BjAAODtAEnIJNjYxMDg2OTMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"62 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1720517160.560970","card_id":"Q_660620571","target":{"id":660620571,"title":"中国有哪些湖景区，大的像海？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/660620571","type":"question","created":1719992906,"answer_count":30,"follower_count":43,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[444,3519935,3530262],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Im833wYDAzMsJEAMaCTEwOTA4MjE4NSDKhJS0BjAAOCtAE3IJNjYwNjIwNTcxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"62 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1720517160.561931","card_id":"Q_659669252","target":{"id":659669252,"title":"大一新生，学计算机是买轻薄本还是游戏本?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/659669252","type":"question","created":1719125384,"answer_count":468,"follower_count":479,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1746,1771,3132,16140,74897],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIm833wYDAzMsJEAMaCTEwODg3MTA0OSCIi9+zBjAAON8DQBRyCTY1OTY2OTI1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b51f5bea6f9f53e0bea061786a371c5a_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1